title: David Hockney American Collectors (Fred and Marcia Weisman) Magnet
description:
Magnet developed from David Hockney’s, American Collectors (Fred and Marcia Weisman), 1968, from The Art Institute of Chicago’s collection. 

Add some artistic flare to your magnetic surfaces with this masterpiece from our collection.

  • Single Magnet
  • Dimensions: 3.5 x 2.5 in.
